{"id": "1447856545491582976", "channel_id": "1447553477638094898", "type": 19, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "yes, but what we talked about is the fact that the the fight is practically impossible for him and pretty hard for random targeting units.\nWith the possible suggestion to make the clones Not Targetable when they become totaly immune to help with that.", "timestamp": "2025-12-09T07:45:00.319000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-09T07:45:07.370000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1131790839291596841"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1447845319223021704", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1447553477638094898", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Doresain targeting issue", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
